Claude Sonnet 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n)\" && git push 2>&1 | tail -2","description":"Commit Step 1 framework state + CANON.md"},"tool_response":{"stdout":"warning: in the working copy of 'Docs/design/CANON.md', LF will be replaced by CRLF the next time Git touches it\n[main 7206590] feat(step1): authoritative framework state on GameState + PlayerState\n 3 files changed, 68 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 Docs/design/CANON.md\nTo https://github.com/Swjsh/Pool-Hop-prj.git\n   f95fcab..7206590  main -> main","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false,"gitOperation":{"commit":{"sha":"7206590","kind":"committed"},"push":{"branch":"main"}}},"tool_use_id":"toolu_01LvqYfz5m6cVajdxfjLMVkZ","duration_ms":4694}
