d standalone launch:\nWASD run + mouse-look camera + Space jump all work.\" && git log --oneline -1","description":"Commit the input fix"},"tool_response":{"stdout":" M Config/DefaultInput.ini\n M Content/Input/Actions/IA_Jump.uasset\n M Content/Input/Actions/IA_Look.uasset\n M Content/Input/Actions/IA_MouseLook.uasset\n M Content/Input/Actions/IA_Move.uasset\n M Content/Input/IMC_Default.uasset\n M Content/Input/IMC_MouseLook.uasset\n?? .claude/btsc-debug.log\nf5c714e fix(input): restore hollow IMC/IA assets from template + engine-level default mapping contexts","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false},"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AY432dRuHVCyGznA6Weqb8","duration_ms":762}
